<H3> <TI>   Rice Export Agreement Signed With Thailand </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Rice Export Agreement Signed With Thailand </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK0106034194 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 
1100 GMT 29 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0106034194 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network </F>
<F P=105>  Vietnamese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Vietnamese Deputy Minister of Trade Nguyen Xuan 
Quang and Thai Deputy Minister of Trade Chaiyot Sasomsap have 
signed an agreement on exchanging information on production, 
marketing, and rice exports. The two sides agreed to exchange 
information on the volume and types of export rice, marketing, 
rice production, and rice export policies on a quarterly and 
yearly basis. The two sides also unanimously agreed to hold a 
ministerial-level meeting once a year and a specialist-level 
meeting twice a year. 

</TEXT>

