  [Text] On the afternoon of 26 May at the reception room of 
the Interior Ministry, Major General A-sang Laoli, minister of 
interior of the Lao People's Democratic Republic [LPDR], 
received a courtesy call from Police General Prathin 
Santipraphop, director general of the Police Department of the 
Interior Ministry of the Kingdom of Thailand, and his entourage. 
