activities of primary state organizations and the living 
standards of the rural population of those Aimaks of Mongolia. 
  The newspaper carries an interview with the Minister of 
External Relations of Mongolia Ts. Gombosuren prior to his 
departure to Cairo for the regular conference of foreign 
ministers of nonaligned countries. 
  The newspaper publishes the text of the national programme 
for the development of health centres resorts and other medical 
recreation institutions of Mongolia having been approved during 
the last sitting of the government of 4 May of the year. 

</TEXT>

