<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Smuggled Goods Discovered on Ship </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK3105053594 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 
0500 GMT 28 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK3105053594 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network </F>
<F P=105>  Vietnamese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Police of Ba Ria-Vung Tau recently started 
prosecution of a smuggling case concerning a ship, the Hoang 
Giang. The ship belongs to the Vietsovpetro joint venture 
enterprise, and was on its way back from a regular repair trip 
in Singapore to Vung Tau. 
  During an administrative inspection, the customs and police 
forces of the province discovered a large amount of merchandise 
that had not been declared to customs and on which taxes had not 
been paid. The lot contains 22 types of items worth over 1 
billion dong. 
  This smuggling case discovered at the sea port of Vung Tau 
is 
a major one. 

</TEXT>

