<TEXT>
Detonators   for Mortars 

<F P=102> 94P30060A </F>
<F P=103> 94P30060A </F>
<F P=104></F>

  CSO 

  [Editorial Report] The 12 April QUAN DOI NHAN DAN reported 
that the Military Region 3 Political-Military School recently 
produced a test run of 35 detonating fuses for 82mm mortar 
rounds. This technical improvement was the idea of Major Nguyen 
Manh Chinh, a cadre at the school. When tested, 100 percent of 
the rounds exploded successfully. The new rounds will be an 
economically effective aid in weapons training. 


