BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 28 (KCNA) -- The U.S. imperialists 
and the South Korean puppets staged a joint air war exercise to 
examine the capacity of a surprise strike on the North in the 
skies above Pyongchang, Hoengsong and Asan bay, South Korea, on 
