<F P=103> SK2705115194 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 27 (KCNA) -- Chairman of the Supreme 
People's Assembly Yang Hyong-sop sent a message of greetings to 
Pius Msekwa upon his election as speaker of the National 
Assembly of the United Republic of Tanzania. 
  Expressing the belief that the friendly and cooperative 
relations between the two parliaments will grow stronger and 
