credit to a project the central Chinese Government is directly 
undertaking," he said. 
  The credits, whose repayment is guaranteed by the World 
Bank, 
is repayable in 10 years after a grace of five years. The 
development bank will formally sign a credit agreement with the 
Chinese Government in Beijing on Sunday, the official added. 

